layout: layouts/base.webc
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<a-masthead></a-masthead>

<style>
    #services {
        margin-block-start: 2em;
    }

    #presentations {
        > div[slot="header"] {
            margin-block-end: 2em;
        }

        div:has(> iframe) {
            padding: 0;
            flex-grow: 0;
            margin-block-end: -7.5px;
        }

        iframe {
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            position: relative !important;
        }
    }

    #posts {
        tag-group {
            font-size: .8em;
        }
    }
</style>

<a-band>
    <a-card bordered featured>
        <p class="headline-summary">Allons-y (<em>ah-lo(n)-zee</em>) is an idiomatic French expression meaning roughly,<br/><strong>"Let's go!"</strong></p>
        <p>That's exactly the energy we bring to design systems work. We help organizations build front-end infrastructure that empowers teamsâ€”transforming design vision into production-ready code while establishing the workflows that make collaboration seamless.</p>
